xt":"Allows to select the balance between result accuracy (precision) and missed barcodes (recall) for linear barcodes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Some barcode types are naturally prone to false positives (e.g. MSI Plessey)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For those barcode types false positives can be drastically reduced (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode","title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"value":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode2Of5Configuration","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode2Of5Configuration\/title"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode2Of5Configuration"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode2Of5Configuration\/fragments"},{"value":[{"text":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode2Of5Configuration","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKBarcodeFormatCode2Of5Configuration\/navigatorTitle"},{"value":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/title"},{"value":[{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/fragments"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text"